Let:
p1(q, x) = ~q /\ ~x
p2(q, x, y) = ~y /\ p1(q, x)
s1(q, x, y, z) = p2(q, x, y) \/ ~z
s2(q, y) = y \/ q

Then:
none(q, x, y, z) = F
all(q, x, y, z) = T
some(q, x, y, z) = p1(q, x)
even_less(q, x, y, z) = p2(q, x, y)
more_than_less(q, x, y, z) = s1(q, x, y, z)
none_again(q, x, y, z) = F
all_again(q, x, y, z) = T
some_again(q, x, y, z) = p1(q, x)
more_than_less_again(q, x, y, z) = s1(q, x, y, z)
half(q, x, y, z) = ~z
some_the_third_time(q, x, y, z) = p1(q, x)
more_than_less_the_third_time(q, x, y, z) = s1(q, x, y, z)
most(q, x, y, z) = s2(q, y)
even_more(q, x, y, z) = ~x \/ s2(q, y)
half_again(q, x, y, z) = ~z
